data.description: Welcome to 2429 Palisade Crest Drive! This barely lived in home was built in 2021 and features 4 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, a study, an oversized game room, and high ceilings throughout the home. The spacious kitchen is perfect for entertaining and features granite countertops, a gas range, and island, and tons of counter space and storage. The kitchen opens up to the 2-story living room, the heart of the home. You will also find a secluded study downstairs off the foyer as well as the owners retreat. Upstairs, you will find three additional bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a game room perfect for game nights or movie nights.
